01:05:49,556 --> 01:05:50,938
Dr. Khalifa: Have you seen that?
Shakira: Yeah.

1125
01:05:51,904 --> 01:05:53,707
Dr. Khalifa: Saint Jude is the health saint.
Shakira: Saint Jude is...?

1126
01:05:54,089 --> 01:05:55,336
Shakira: Oh, the saint of health.

1127
01:05:55,336 --> 01:06:03,265
Dr. Khalifa: Right. And... so, God is saying here they were really
idolizing nothing because Saint Jude is dead,

1128
01:06:03,265 --> 01:06:09,303
powerless, he knows nothing about the surgery,
never heard of it, and probably Saint Jude himself never existed.

1129
01:06:09,303 --> 01:06:10,006
Shakira: Yeah.

1130
01:06:10,006 --> 01:06:12,017
Dr. Khalifa: Some of those saints are fictional.

1131
01:06:12,884 --> 01:06:14,508
We find out now.

1132
01:06:15,373 --> 01:06:16,755
A woman: (unintelligible)

1133
01:06:19,320 --> 01:06:22,801
Dr. Khalifa: Okay, so those who set up idols besides God
are really following nothing.

1134
01:06:22,801 --> 01:06:27,063
Because even if Saint Jude is alive, he has
no power over the surgery that you are doing.

1135
01:06:27,063 --> 01:06:27,951
Shakira: Yeah.

1136
01:06:27,951 --> 01:06:29,191
Dr. Khalifa: He has nothing to do with it.

1137
01:06:29,191 --> 01:06:29,691
Shakira: Yeah.

1138
01:06:30,000 --> 01:06:33,841
Dr. Khalifa: So, they are following nothing. They only follow conjecture. They only guess.

1139
01:06:34,706 --> 01:06:42,573
[10:67]  He is the One who rendered the night for your rest, and rendered the day lighted. These are proofs for people who can hear.

1140
01:06:43,749 --> 01:06:46,838
When you think of night and day, what are
we talking about?

1141
01:06:46,838 --> 01:06:54,023
We're talking about the planet Earth hanging
in space and rotating like this so the sunlight creates day and night.

1142
01:06:55,191 --> 01:06:56,191
Dr. Khalifa: Are you okay?

1143
01:06:56,191 --> 01:07:02,874
Shakira: Yeah, I'm getting a lot of shocks. I'm feeling, I am feeling so bad that I created the mistake. I feel like...

1144
01:07:02,874 --> 01:07:03,914
Dr. Khalifa: Which mistake?

1145
01:07:03,914 --> 01:07:04,954
Shakira: This mistake.

1146
01:07:06,023 --> 01:07:06,904
Dr. Khalifa: Oh, I see.

1147
01:07:06,904 --> 01:07:11,953
Shakira: I don't want to be in this world because I am so mad.
Dr. Khalifa: Well, aren't you glad you're given a chance to do that?

1148
01:07:12,485 --> 01:07:15,274
Dr. Khalifa: This is exactly why God brought you here.
Shakira: Yeah, but it's getting too much to me.

1149
01:07:15,274 --> 01:07:18,015
Dr. Khalifa: Yeah, so you can denounce...You're denouncing it now.

1150
01:07:18,015 --> 01:07:24,400
Shakira: I am so shocked at these human people who
are not realizing His presence.
Dr. Khalifa: Yes. Yes.

1151
01:07:24,400 --> 01:07:27,944
Dr. Khalifa: This was one Khutba. I have to send you the video.
Shakira: (unintelligible)

1152
01:07:28,253 --> 01:07:32,044
Dr. Khalifa: This, I have to send you the video of this, one Khutba three weeks back.

1153
01:07:32,353 --> 01:07:35,897
Dr. Khalifa: The title was "How Bad the Human Being Is and
How Fortunate We Are."

1154
01:07:35,897 --> 01:07:37,897
Shakira: I want to go on the streets and shout.

1155
01:07:38,453 --> 01:07:40,824
Shakira: "Listen to God. Listen to God."
Dr. Khalifa: Yeah.

1156
01:07:41,997 --> 01:07:45,417
I want to tell my mother like this "Listen to God."

1157
01:07:45,417 --> 01:07:47,664
Parivash: "Wake up."
Dr. Khalifa: Now, cool down. Cool down.

1158
01:07:47,664 --> 01:07:49,170
Dr. Khalifa: Your aunt is worried about you.

1159
01:07:50,158 --> 01:07:52,158
Dr. Khalifa: Yes. See, what I am telling her?
A woman: No, why me?

1160
01:07:52,158 --> 01:07:53,540
Dr. Khalifa: "Cool down, Shakira."
Parivash: Yeah, cool down.

1161
01:07:53,540 --> 01:07:56,219
Shakira: But I'm not mad. I am so stable.

1162
01:07:56,219 --> 01:08:00,000
A woman: No, I am not thinking anything... First, I have to know.

1163
01:08:00,371 --> 01:08:04,718
Shakira: No, no, but for me, I am so excited for me.
A woman: And then, I have (unintelligible) I heard. That's why I am listening.

1164
01:08:04,718 --> 01:08:07,891
Dr. Khalifa: Yes. Mã Shã Allãh. She's just too enthusiastic.

1165
01:08:08,385 --> 01:08:15,000
A woman: She is always, I am telling, she is enthusiastic. Whatever the person is. Not only today.

1166
01:08:15,000 --> 01:08:15,500
Dr. Khalifa: Yes.

1167
01:08:15,500 --> 01:08:17,500
Dr. Khalifa: This is the big one.
A woman: She's always... Yeah.
Shakira: No, but not (unintelligible).

1168
01:08:17,871 --> 01:08:20,489
A woman: This is a big shock. This is a big shock, maybe.
Dr. Khalifa: This is the real thing. Yes.

1169
01:08:20,983 --> 01:08:22,551
A woman: She had so many shocks before.

1170
01:08:22,860 --> 01:08:23,995
A woman: Yeah.
Shakira: Yeah.

1171
01:08:23,995 --> 01:08:27,354
Dr. Khalifa: But this is, this is the fantastic realization.

1172
01:08:28,898 --> 01:08:31,269
It's where it comes with the, with the proof.

1173
01:08:31,887 --> 01:08:33,887
Dr. Khalifa: But I am telling her to cool down. Cool down.

1174
01:08:33,887 --> 01:08:34,590
A woman: Yeah.

1175
01:08:34,590 --> 01:08:36,466
A woman: That's, you have to make her.

1176
01:08:36,466 --> 01:08:37,169
Dr. Khalifa: Yes.

1177
01:08:37,169 --> 01:08:40,651
A woman: Then, God...
Parivash: Messenger of God tells you that you have to be cool down and...

1178
01:08:40,651 --> 01:08:41,354
A woman: Calm down.

1179
01:08:41,354 --> 01:08:43,354
Shakira: But cool down doesn't mean that I can't,
Parivash: You have to obey.

1180
01:08:43,354 --> 01:08:45,000
Shakira: I shouldn't go out.
A woman: No, no, not
Parivash: No.

1181
01:08:45,000 --> 01:08:46,753
A woman: Not your mind. Relax.
Dr. Khalifa: Relax. To relax.

1182
01:08:46,753 --> 01:08:49,247
Shakira: Cool down for myself so I feel better about..., right?
Parivash: Relax.

1183
01:08:49,247 --> 01:08:50,568
Dr. Khalifa: Yeah.
Parivash: Yeah, when you talk, relax.

1184
01:08:50,568 --> 01:08:55,508
Dr. Khalifa: Cause not everybody is as enthusiastic as you are.
A woman: See, you shouldn't be emotional in talking and everything.

1185
01:08:55,508 --> 01:08:57,763
A woman: Then, there will be mistakes.
Parivash: Yeah.
Dr. Khalifa: Yes, exactly.

1186
01:08:57,763 --> 01:09:01,243
A woman: You have to calm down and slowly, you have to teach people.
Dr. Khalifa: Cool. Yes.

1187
01:09:01,243 --> 01:09:03,127
A woman: Then, only they will find...
Dr. Khalifa: Yes.

1188
01:09:03,127 --> 01:09:06,284
Dr. Khalifa: You do exactly what you want, only more effectively.
A woman: Yeah.

1189
01:09:06,284 --> 01:09:08,146
Dr. Khalifa: Calm down is a very good thing.
A woman: Yeah.

1190
01:09:08,455 --> 01:09:09,158
Shakira: Yeah.

1191
01:09:09,158 --> 01:09:11,282
Dr. Khalifa: Calm down and see.
Parivash: I was exactly like you.

1192
01:09:11,282 --> 01:09:13,282
Dr. Khalifa: Exactly. Yes.
Shakira: How long now?
Parivash: Yes.

1193
01:09:13,838 --> 01:09:15,282
Parivash: Huh?
Shakira: How long it took you?
Dr. Khalifa: Three, four years.

1194
01:09:15,282 --> 01:09:16,788
A woman: Three, four years?! My God.

1195
01:09:18,085 --> 01:09:19,529
Parivash: Now, I am relaxed.

1196
01:09:19,900 --> 01:09:22,332
Shakira: Three, four years!
Parivash: Yeah, I was really hyped, you know.
Dr. Khalifa: Yeah.

1197
01:09:22,332 --> 01:09:24,332
Dr. Khalifa: Yeah.
Shakira: Me, too.
Parivash: I went as soon as I came back from...

1198
01:09:24,332 --> 01:09:27,492
Dr. Khalifa: She wanted to go on the streets and shout at the people.
Shakira: Me, too, all the time, you know.

1199
01:09:27,492 --> 01:09:31,344
Parivash: You know, you know what's
happening. Every time, you know. I went to my neighbor.
Shakira: Me, too.

1200
01:09:31,344 --> 01:09:33,344
Parivash: He's Jewish. I say "you know what's happening?"

1201
01:09:33,344 --> 01:09:35,344
Shakira: Ask her (unintelligible)
Parivash: We are same. We are same.

1202
01:09:35,344 --> 01:09:36,665
Dr. Khalifa: Listen, listen, you're gonna laugh at this.

1203
01:09:36,665 --> 01:09:37,245
Parivash: Yeah.

1204
01:09:37,245 --> 01:09:41,035
Dr. Khalifa: Somebody is in the street lost about the address. And they come and knock on her door.
Parivash: Yeah.

1205
01:09:41,035 --> 01:09:47,173
Dr. Khalifa: "Is this where Mr. So-and-so", then Parivash "come in, come in. Do you know that God sent a message that it's mathematically coded?"

1206
01:09:48,779 --> 01:09:54,793
"And we now have proof that tells us where we're going wrong and how we can correct it and how we go to Heaven."

1207
01:09:55,164 --> 01:09:57,164
The woman is coming to ask about an address.

1208
01:09:58,646 --> 01:10:00,646
Dr. Khalifa: And this happened when I was there.

1209
01:10:00,646 --> 01:10:02,399
Shakira: I'm doing the same thing.

1210
01:10:02,399 --> 01:10:03,781
Parivash: Yeah.
Dr. Khalifa: Of course. Exactly.

1211
01:10:04,275 --> 01:10:06,954
Dr. Khalifa: How do you think Naoko is here? Why do you think Naoko is here?

1212
01:10:07,327 --> 01:10:13,247
They were going in the same class studying English and Naoko came to say "how do you say this word?", for example.

1213
01:10:13,699 --> 01:10:16,157
And she said "did you know that God sent a message?"

1214
01:10:17,577 --> 01:10:18,817
And Naoko said "what?"

1215
01:10:19,496 --> 01:10:19,996
Parivash: Yeah but...

1216
01:10:19,996 --> 01:10:23,894
She said "God sent a message that's mathematically coded."
Naoko said "really? What is that?"

1217
01:10:23,894 --> 01:10:25,574
She said "come to my house."

1218
01:10:27,555 --> 01:10:30,966
Dr. Khalifa: This is how it happened.
Parivash: And at that time, we couldn't talk even English.

1219
01:10:30,966 --> 01:10:31,466
Dr. Khalifa: Right.

1220
01:10:31,466 --> 01:10:36,173
Parivash: Because it was very low class in English.
We couldn't talk in English, but we understand each other.

1221
01:10:36,173 --> 01:10:39,612
Dr. Khalifa: And I bear witness to this. Naoko didn't know any English, and Parivash didn't know any English.

1222
01:10:39,612 --> 01:10:45,861
A woman: Yeah. Housekeeper, she don't know any English. I'm trying hard. But we are trying our best to contact with her.
Dr. Khalifa: Communicate.

1223
01:10:45,861 --> 01:10:48,293
Parivash: If you want, God wants.
A woman: Yeah. Yeah.
Shakira: Yeah.

1224
01:10:49,158 --> 01:10:52,764
Parivash: Yeah but to say... Yeah.
A woman: Because the heart is good, we can communicate.

1225
01:10:52,764 --> 01:10:55,629
Dr. Khalifa: But there's nothing wrong with you. In fact, there is something right with you.
Shakira: I know but...

1226
01:10:55,629 --> 01:11:02,323
A woman: Yeah.
Shakira: But my mother keeps telling me, and my husband
keeps telling me that I have to contain myself.

1227
01:11:02,323 --> 01:11:07,781
Shakira: I shouldn't talk about this to anybody. I have to do it only to myself. And I should, you know,...
Dr. Khalifa: Yes.

1228
01:11:08,028 --> 01:11:12,251
Parivash: Actually, my husband, he doesn't want to see any of this.
A woman: They say "you need not create enemies."

1229
01:11:12,554 --> 01:11:13,594
Dr. Khalifa: Yes.

1230
01:11:13,594 --> 01:11:19,238
A woman: Going and telling disbelievers who argue with you. Just tell.
Dr. Khalifa: You made them nervous. But put on a facade of calmness.

1231
01:11:19,547 --> 01:11:20,868
A woman: Just tell them.
Parivash: Yeah. Just tell them.

1232
01:11:20,868 --> 01:11:24,149
A woman: Whether they believe or not, that is God's will.
Parivash: Yeah. Yeah. Just tell them.

1233
01:11:24,149 --> 01:11:28,619
A woman: You shouldn't force them to do...
Shakira: No, but Damesh tells me I cannot talk to anybody. He says I shouldn't talk.

1234
01:11:28,619 --> 01:11:31,051
Shakira: He says "you should become..."
A woman: No, talk (unintelligible)

1235
01:11:31,051 --> 01:11:39,289
A woman: Don't, don't start and create problems like you talk to your friend Piyush, and she's against you like that.
Shakira: Yeah, he told me... But I didn't talk badly to her.

1236
01:11:39,289 --> 01:11:40,486
Shakira: That is the problem.
A woman: Yeah.

1237
01:11:40,486 --> 01:11:44,586
Shakira: I just gave her the book, and she got upset.
Dr. Khalifa: Yes. Right.

1238
01:11:44,586 --> 01:11:50,292
Shakira: I gave her only the book.
A woman: Not just book but you were arguing about these matters and she got upset and (unintelligible)
Dr. Khalifa: She has to get upset.

1239
01:11:50,292 --> 01:11:52,107
Shakira: I never argued with her.

1240
01:11:52,107 --> 01:11:53,843
Shakira: God is my witness.
A woman: Calm down. Calm down.

1241
01:11:53,843 --> 01:11:55,596
Shakira: I know, but I never argued with her.

1242
01:11:55,596 --> 01:11:57,596
Dr. Khalifa: Well, I believe that because it happens frequently.

1243
01:11:57,596 --> 01:12:02,005
Dr. Khalifa: Sometimes, we're just giving the message very quietly and very nicely, but they become up in arms.
Shakira: Just giving the book to them.
A woman & Parivash: Yeah.

1244
01:12:02,005 --> 01:12:05,178
A woman: Even though, I don't know here before, I was telling
her.

1245
01:12:05,178 --> 01:12:06,375
Shakira: I don't know him, too.

1246
01:12:06,375 --> 01:12:13,563
A woman: Be calm down and teach them whatever you know. Let them listen or not, that's not your business.
Dr. Khalifa: Yes.

1247
01:12:14,304 --> 01:12:14,804
Shakira: But...

1248
01:12:14,804 --> 01:12:17,175
Dr. Khalifa: Yes. But what I'm saying is sometimes you can't help it.
A woman: Isn't it? When the soil is,...

1249
01:12:17,175 --> 01:12:19,978
A woman: When the soil is fertile, the seed will grow.

1250
01:12:19,978 --> 01:12:21,978
A woman: The seed will germinate.
Dr. Khalifa: Yes. I went though this myself.

1251
01:12:21,978 --> 01:12:29,536
Dr. Khalifa: Sometimes I just, in the gentlest possible way, I just give them the message and they'll become terribly upset.
Shakira & a woman: Yeah.

1252
01:12:30,462 --> 01:12:35,365
Shakira: He's telling even if you talk nicely, people
sometimes they are so fanatical...
A woman: Yeah, but you should be like that.

1253
01:12:35,365 --> 01:12:41,997
A woman: You are a messenger, that's why you should
be calm and still. You should have patience.
Dr. Khalifa: Yes. Exactly.

1254
01:12:41,997 --> 01:12:45,726
Shakira: How do I know how he was? Maybe 20 years ago, he would scream at them.

1255
01:12:46,529 --> 01:12:54,396
Shakira: Because (unintelligible), I don't know. But with time, so patient. 20 years, maybe 20 years from now, I will be...
Dr. Khalifa: Yes. It's true. Yes.

1256
01:12:54,396 --> 01:12:56,643
A woman: That means there is some weakness in the messenger.

1257
01:12:56,643 --> 01:12:58,643
Shakira: Right? It takes time and...

1258
01:12:58,643 --> 01:12:59,161
Parivash: Yes.

1259
01:12:59,161 --> 01:13:03,755
A woman: There shouldn't be...
Shakira: Even to become a messenger and become a good
messenger, it takes time.

1260
01:13:03,755 --> 01:13:04,396
A woman: Yeah.

1261
01:13:04,396 --> 01:13:06,396
Dr. Khalifa: It takes time. Yes.

1262
01:13:07,569 --> 01:13:10,866
Shakira: Yes.
Parivash: God willing. IN SHAA ALLAH.
A woman: Even people listening and all those,

1263
01:13:10,866 --> 01:13:15,398
A woman: it is their capacity to understand.
Shakira: But I want to reach the majority.

1264
01:13:15,398 --> 01:13:16,966
Shakira: I want us to reach the majority.

1265
01:13:16,966 --> 01:13:20,695
Shakira: And I think a better way than to hand out
this book is talking for the first time.

1266
01:13:20,695 --> 01:13:23,560
Dr. Khalifa: You're doing very good with those college...
Shakira: That's what we should do.

1267
01:13:23,560 --> 01:13:25,745
A woman: And also, I want... Excuse me.
Dr. Khalfia: Yes. Wonderful.

1268
01:13:26,116 --> 01:13:28,857
A woman: And also I want... First, you refine yourself.

1269
01:13:30,000 --> 01:13:30,827
A woman: Calm down.

1270
01:13:31,568 --> 01:13:34,927
Shakira: Aunt, I refine myself...
A woman: Leave the anger and everything.

1271
01:13:34,927 --> 01:13:44,647
A woman: Unless you do those things first, you cannot preach or you cannot tell people. You should be the one that shows an example, isn't it?

1272
01:13:45,265 --> 01:13:50,971
Dr. Khalifa: Right, but you see, like I said, sometimes...
A woman: If somebody (unintelligible) and says "oh,
Shakira is doing like that, but she is preaching like this."

1273
01:13:50,971 --> 01:13:52,156
A woman: It shouldn't be like that.

1274
01:13:52,156 --> 01:13:55,761
Dr. Khalifa: No, did you hear... it's not what she said, that she...
Shakira: First, how can I be a good Muslim the way I am.

1275
01:13:55,761 --> 01:14:00,293
Dr. Khalifa: All she did was give them the book.
A woman: Not good Muslim, good person. You said "good person is enough."
Shakira: Yes. I'm a bad person.

1276
01:14:00,293 --> 01:14:07,407
Dr. Khalifa: Shakira, you know, what they feel, it's the ego again.
A woman: No, not that.

1277
01:14:07,407 --> 01:14:08,295
A woman: Yeah.

1278
01:14:08,295 --> 01:14:10,974
Dr. Khalifa: Where you're telling them that everything you were doing was wrong.
A woman: Yeah.

1279
01:14:10,974 --> 01:14:13,839
Dr. Khalifa: "Me?! Everything I was doing was wrong."
A woman: Yeah. That's what creates enemies.

1280
01:14:13,839 --> 01:14:18,001
Dr. Khalifa: But she can be, no, but she can be very diplomatic and very nice and this will still happen.

1281
01:14:18,001 --> 01:14:25,868
You just show them this and it says, for example,
"the first pillar of Islam is 'I bear witness that God is the only god.'"

1282
01:14:26,424 --> 01:14:30,833
Now, the Muslims, in 1400 years, they added,
"and I bear witness that Muhammad is His messenger."

1283
01:14:31,451 --> 01:14:33,451
The Quran says that this is idolatry.

1284
01:14:33,451 --> 01:14:35,451
You should not put any name next to God.

1285
01:14:36,130 --> 01:14:40,600
So, what she's telling her mother is that
the first pillar that she has been practicing is wrong.

1286
01:14:41,094 --> 01:14:42,785
And this gets them all upset.

1287
01:14:42,785 --> 01:14:44,600
Dr. Khalifa: And she can do this in the nicest way.

1288
01:14:44,600 --> 01:14:48,453
Shakira: I have done it in the nicest way. I am nice to them.
A woman: Yeah.
Dr. Khalifa: But it still... yeah.

1289
01:14:48,453 --> 01:14:53,603
Dr. Khalifa: But still upsets them because all of a sudden
they realize that all their life they've been doing something wrong.

1290
01:14:53,603 --> 01:14:55,109
Shakira: I'm talking nicely...

1291
01:14:55,109 --> 01:14:57,480
Dr. Khalifa: And they don't take it in a nice way.

1292
01:14:57,480 --> 01:15:00,530
Shakira: I have changed so much. Really, I have changed.
Dr. Khalifa: This makes them very upset.

1293
01:15:00,530 --> 01:15:01,030
Dr. Khalifa: Yes.

1294
01:15:01,030 --> 01:15:07,230
Shakira: But what is happening is that even if I am talking to them in the nicest way, they still
Dr. Khalifa: Still we know this. Yes.

1295
01:15:07,230 --> 01:15:10,280
Shakira: are being mean to me because they think that I am...
A woman: Not mean.

1296
01:15:10,280 --> 01:15:13,021
Shakira: Yes, my mother is mean to me.
A woman: You want suddenly to change them.

1297
01:15:13,268 --> 01:15:16,503
Shakira: No, I don't want to change them.
A woman: The change isn't suddenly. Because you change...

1298
01:15:16,503 --> 01:15:17,391
Shakira: They blame me for everything.

1299
01:15:17,391 --> 01:15:19,391
Shakira: I don't want to suddenly change them.
A woman: No, no. Not blame. Disapprove.

1300
01:15:19,391 --> 01:15:24,973
A woman: Your nature is you can believe whatever you
believe suddenly. But everybody is not so fast.
Shakira: No, my nature has nothing to do with it anymore.

1301
01:15:24,973 --> 01:15:26,108
Dr. Khalifa: Yes. True.

1302
01:15:26,108 --> 01:15:27,120
A woman: You shouldn't get angry with them.

